sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente
    participant AS as Authorization Server

    C->>C: generar code_verifier
    C->>C: calcular code_challenge = BASE64URL(SHA-256(code_verifier))
    C->>AS: /authorize + code_challenge + method=S256
    AS-->>C: authorization_code
    C->>AS: /token + authorization_code + code_verifier
    AS->>AS: validar code_verifier contra code_challenge
    AS-->>C: tokens
